  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You conjure a large seal upon the ground, causing numerous purple tentacles made of pure energy to arise. All hostile creatures within 5 feet of you must succeed a Dexterity saving throw or be pulled to the ground, being knocked prone and unable to make Hand Signs until the end of their next turn.</p><p>If you use a <em><strong>Brave Order</strong></em> to cast this Art, you can increase the radius to 10 feet and impose a -1d4 penalty to affected creatures.</p>",
